        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 element-animate">
                <div class="media d-block media-custom text-left">
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <h3 class="mt-0 text-black"><a href="#" class="text-black">Diagnosis</a></h3>
                        <p>Hi,Sorry to say but you are diagnosed with <span class="text-black"> Diabetes Type 2</span>. Though there's nothing to worry about. Special care and medications can treat and can give relief upto great extent. Here are some test suggestions for you to have it for clearer view of the disease you are having. Thanks. </p>

                    </div>
                </div>
