                    <div class="media-body">
                        <h3 class="mt-0 text-black"><a href="#" class="text-black">Causes</a></h3>
                        <p>Here's the list of causes due to which you are diagnosed with <span class="text-black">Diabetes Type 2</span> </p>
                        <p>overweight</p>
                        <p>obesity</p>
                        <p>lack of physical activity</p>
                        <p>insulin resistence</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 element-animate">
                <div class="media d-block media-custom text-left">
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <h3 class="mt-0 text-black"><a href="#" class="text-black">Tests</a></h3>
                        <p>Here's the list of tests you need to take within few days to get better picture of the disease and to start treatment at earliest. </p>
                        <p>Sugar test</p>
                        <p>Blood pressure</p>
                        <p>Urine test</p>
                        <p>Skin thickness test</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 element-animate">
                <div class="media d-block media-custom text-left">
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <h3 class="mt-0 text-black"><a href="#" class="text-black">Suggestions</a></h3>
                        <p>Here's the list of actions/medicines you can take to relieve some of your pain from <span class="text-black">Diabetes Type 2</span> </p>
